Package: PLMScoRe
Type: Package
Title: Derives PLM and other indices according to WASM rules
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(person("Stephany", "Fulda", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "stephany.fulda@gmail.com"))
Author: Stephany Fulda
Maintainer: Stephany Fulda <stephany.fulda@gmail.com>
Description: PLMScoRe will take information about leg movements, sleep, arousal, and respiratory events
    as input and returns descriptive statistics/indices about leg movement activity including 
    intermovement interval plots and PLM indices. At the moment only REMLogic event txt files are the supported
    input. For more information see https://github.com/Steph-Fulda/PLMScoRe/wiki
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Steph-Fulda/PLMScoRe
